    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> I'm really glad you went on and implement HOC :) Looks very good! (made a suggestion though ;)\n\nYes this is a nice pattern that we should maybe talk about a little in a blog post. This is very different from Component extend AnotherComponent as we talked because inheritance do not allow the Parent to control the render() behavior. While when compositing you can. And this is what we needed here.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-09-25T10:50:51Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/130#issuecomment-143185977",
