    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@vvo any chance in the future that the hits widget will receive a header footer option?\nUse case would be to include a link at the bottom of results, that you want to show ONLY if results.\n\nRight now the hits container when it first gets results will remove any html set within the element, instead of appending/prepending it.\n",
