    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@Giovanni-Mattucci Best way to do that right no would be to:\n\n``` js\nvar search = instantsearch...\nvar hideWhenNoHits = {\n  render: function(params) {\n    if (params.hits.length === 0) {\n      // hide some div\n    }\n  }\n};\n\nsearch.addWidget(hideWhenNoHits);\n```\n",
