  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@vvo awesome thanks for putting me in the right direction! Got it to work exactly as I wanted.\n\nJust an update to your snippet there:\n\n``` javascript\nvar search = instantsearch...\nvar hideWhenNoHits = {\n  render: function(params) {\n    if (params.results.hits.length === 0) {\n      // hide some div\n    }\n  }\n};\nsearch.addWidget(hideWhenNoHits);\n```\n\n:)\n",
